The tests in this directory tree were vendored from the Chromium project.
Do NOT modify these tests directly in WebKit.
Instead, send a pull request to the WICG/html-in-canvas explainer:
	https://github.com/WICG/html-in-canvas
or to the live spec PR:
	https://github.com/whatwg/html/pull/11588

These tests are not part of upstream web-platform-tests; they live in
Chromium's `wpt_internal/` tree until the spec is upstreamed. They were
imported manually (not via Tools/Scripts/import-w3c-tests, which only
syncs upstream WPT). The carve-out is recorded in
`LayoutTests/imported/w3c/resources/import-expectations.json` so a
re-sync of upstream WPT does NOT delete this subtree.

Do NOT modify or remove this file.

